                        <item xml:id="e1">- Fol. 3r, in the upper margin. Unfinished note, apparently a continuation of Additio 1 containing condemnation of those attempting to damage the Ms.&#xD;
- Fols. 20v, 25v, 56v, 61r, 87r, 94r, 124v, in the upper margin. Crude notes indicating the texts beginning in the respective folios.&#xD;
- Fols. 34r, 35r, 38r, 60v, 70r, in the upper margin. Pen trials.&#xD;
- Fol. 47r, in the upper margin: doodles.</item>
